    "body": "script to import validator folder containing *.json and *.txt\r\n```sh\r\n#!/bin/bash\r\n\r\ndirPath=/root/oonoonba_validators/tranch3\r\ndirPathLen=${#dirPath}\r\necho \"length=${dirPathLen}\"\r\n\r\n\r\nfor file in \"${dirPath}\"/*.json;do\r\n  json=${file:dirPathLen+1:98}\r\n  pw=$( cat $dirPath/$json.txt )\r\n\r\n  echo ${pw} | ./bin/lodestar account validator import --keystore ${dirPath}/${json}.json --network oonoonba\r\ndone\r\n```\r\ngot\r\n```\r\nroot@vmi512326:~/lodestar/packages/cli# ./bin/lodestar account validator list --network oonoonba | wc -l\r\n400\r\n```",
